msgctxt "56_Saejima"
msgid "Tadashi?"
msgstr "¿Tadashi?"

msgctxt "68_Tadashi"
msgid "I'm gonna go get my sister!"
msgstr "¡Voy a ir a buscar a mi hermana!"

msgctxt "80_Saejima"
msgid "Don't underestimate the yakuza, boy. Whaddya think you'll accomplish on your lonesome?"
msgstr "No subestimes a la yakuza, chico. ¿Qué piensas hacer yendo tú solo?"

msgctxt "92_Tadashi"
msgid "Rescuing my sister, that's what. I know I can do it!"
msgstr "Rescatar a mi hermana, eso haré. ¡Sé que puedo!"

msgctxt "116_Saejima"
msgid "Tadashi!"
msgstr "¡Tadashi!"

msgctxt "128_Saejima"
msgid "(Damn that boy, jumpin' the gun like that. He'll get his ass kicked on his own.)"
msgstr "(Maldición, ese chico es muy impulsivo. Solo conseguirá\n"\n"que le pateen el culo.)"

msgctxt "140_Saejima"
msgid "(Best go to the Takasu Family office down Theater Alley and reel the kid in!)"
msgstr "(¡Será mejor que vaya a la oficina de la familia Takasu\n"\n"en el Callejón del teatro y alcanzarlo!)"

